                "updated": {
                    "$t": "2026-01-17T02:07:38.364-08:00"
                },
                "title": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "$t": "My world (MOM)"
                },
                "content": {
                    "type": "html",
                    "$t": "<div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style=\"font-family: times;\"><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">My world; place in the story was my mom</span></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: times;\"><br /></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: times;\"><br /></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: times;\"><br /></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: times;\"><br /></span></div><div><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgSnDODyEYF1ye2EvJ6OTxa-zEOs4MPItGeGl45p6iomGi7BH4YUpKvjtWv4379Yh6dupk45O_prakUQ4tefLI4j6ZRFvuzh3RyDJmsLssQ8RVzzTYoqs6iV9qebtbMolK9xFBxz5m0lGG39_XVAMptVXCozoeD61C_4473Ev1wZ6ibgpuVrKtjHOuEuKU\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"1690\" data-original-width=\"940\" height=\"384\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgSnDODyEYF1ye2EvJ6OTxa-zEOs4MPItGeGl45p6iomGi7BH4YUpKvjtWv4379Yh6dupk45O_prakUQ4tefLI4j6ZRFvuzh3RyDJmsLssQ8RVzzTYoqs6iV9qebtbMolK9xFBxz5m0lGG39_XVAMptVXCozoeD61C_4473Ev1wZ6ibgpuVrKtjHOuEuKU=w485-h384\" width=\"485\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></td></tr></tbody></table><br /></div><div><span style=\"font-family: times;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">She was not only my mom but&nbsp; an angel who beautifully create my world</span></span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">The story begins here,</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">when i was small i thought world is a beautiful place to be in</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">But i was unaware of the troubles which lives brings being in the world</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">Slowly everything i enjoyed passing of time and my age with my mom</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">I grew younger and mom grew older&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">I could not notice the changes that was taking place with my world</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">I thought my mom is my strength she will never be away leaving me alone&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">But one day for my higher study i went away from my mom&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">But i thought where will she go she will be with me being my world</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">After the study completed and dreams was in the pick i made my mind to be back to home</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">Yes, i was in home after several waits and finally i met my mom&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">The happiness of meeting her blooms my day with her smile and blessing of fate</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">Just evening appeared sun was drawn, and family times begin</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">All were enjoying till nothing happened&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">Everything was better fine till the mom didn't respond&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">A sudden call rang which changed my world</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">There was silence and heaviness inside the heart&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times;\">It was nothing but everything a last goodbye of my world which was my mom</span></div><div><span style=\"color: red;\"><br /></span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div>"
                },
