                    "$t": "Unexplained exception."
                },
                "content": {
                    "type": "html",
                    "$t": "<p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjlxqFOC1gNzwccu8ZipqN3gAfnWDUewCfpgWIb6jjAPvVHxDrbyVKL9Z93PL-hm3DoFJuTCCkTeSfXifvZ5aGASWVkXzBi2fZs6Yhn-681PBxfFzAMTDyBbHLqyWGvtMNeQP2ZwRzu5LExWOlq-RxE4Cp2c88ERro5ZGVtEweQ8yKoosJJx-PV5-GLHMQ\" style=\"background-color: #fff2cc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"554\" data-original-width=\"600\" height=\"185\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjlxqFOC1gNzwccu8ZipqN3gAfnWDUewCfpgWIb6jjAPvVHxDrbyVKL9Z93PL-hm3DoFJuTCCkTeSfXifvZ5aGASWVkXzBi2fZs6Yhn-681PBxfFzAMTDyBbHLqyWGvtMNeQP2ZwRzu5LExWOlq-RxE4Cp2c88ERro5ZGVtEweQ8yKoosJJx-PV5-GLHMQ=w200-h185\" width=\"200\" /></a></div><br /><p></p><p><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>I thought to be perfect in the sense of perfection</b></div><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>But I didn't realized it was unexplained exception</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>I fairy tailed of love from everyone</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>But I didn't know it was the hate of someone</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Trying to be perfect was okey</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>But trying to be flawless was not</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>I admired slowly everyone was not as perfect as we stare out</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>It was just a rotation of time with ongoing rhyme</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>At the end of state it was just a realization never stop to be good</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>whatever be the situation with unexplained exception</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b><br /></b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b><br /></b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p><br /></p><blockquote style=\"border: none; margin: 0 0 0 40px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p></blockquote><p><br /></p>"
