                "title": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "$t": "Beautiful life"
                },
                "content": {
                    "type": "html",
                    "$t": "<p><br /></p><p>Glorious feel of life&nbsp;</p><p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjXIG-7q7UkEQ-2jFrXMxqjmCvEV50MSKj1A8sMajLtU2JWLdB865t8gjuERojEWokNVV7nlnmaU6fdE6cNXvQgsB0I8SBHM5Vf6t7TW8dC0aDuIOrfk2BhHKMOue4N2fL-q6yqUbt1B1XzvORohrT44mv29r4BKkXmvsPW-2YCtqlZa3lJLljZ0If0\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"700\" data-original-width=\"933\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjXIG-7q7UkEQ-2jFrXMxqjmCvEV50MSKj1A8sMajLtU2JWLdB865t8gjuERojEWokNVV7nlnmaU6fdE6cNXvQgsB0I8SBHM5Vf6t7TW8dC0aDuIOrfk2BhHKMOue4N2fL-q6yqUbt1B1XzvORohrT44mv29r4BKkXmvsPW-2YCtqlZa3lJLljZ0If0=w571-h324\" width=\"571\" /></a></div><span style=\"color: red;\"><br /><i style=\"font-family: times; font-size: large;\">once upon a morning what i see was the fairy with sparkling light</i></span><p></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>With a blooms of flower cherishing the weather all the side</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>I was wonder with seeing the beauty of the sky and asking self was it a night or a beautiful life</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>I cannot believe in my eyes was it true or just a imagination alike</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>I saw a bird singing in the roof with enlightenment of the joy&nbsp;</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>I felt a rain droplets with full of shine in a beautiful sky</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>Still i was wonder was it true or just a imagination alike</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>The things went so beautiful that i was mesmerizing with the joy</i></span></p><p><span style=\"color: red; font-family: times; font-size: medium;\"><i>And it was feel like was it a beautiful life.. :) :)</i></span></p><p><br /></p>"
                },
