                "content": {
                    "type": "html",
                    "$t": "<p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhyadkBS14iKnP82Xd-5Nd77lUc0S-rjvlh83vwVxw1NaY4H5GVEq0nERYE3Hr0dTl9inoaL760qke0BGBhV1Iu_ioPoaEA18oTea-xkD30aXAxMFNSmFjn49LaKmR3DEQkLRfb3sXGgkipZn9z46M-yzNpHUOEQgi-pjGaAMiuR2Eyjgqg6k_4Nvrd\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"672\" data-original-width=\"1024\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhyadkBS14iKnP82Xd-5Nd77lUc0S-rjvlh83vwVxw1NaY4H5GVEq0nERYE3Hr0dTl9inoaL760qke0BGBhV1Iu_ioPoaEA18oTea-xkD30aXAxMFNSmFjn49LaKmR3DEQkLRfb3sXGgkipZn9z46M-yzNpHUOEQgi-pjGaAMiuR2Eyjgqg6k_4Nvrd=w497-h240\" width=\"497\" /></a></div><br /><br /><p></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <b>&nbsp; &nbsp; The hope of ray</b></p><p><br /></p><p>&nbsp;<i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">Once a time, a storming rain occurs with a night</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">&nbsp;everything went with a flow, nothing was left behind</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">when night passes and a day rise with a sunshine</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">a people were feeling tenses with full of their minds</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">people went here and there collecting things and stuff&nbsp;</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">but nothing could happen rather than rain disturbed</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">the struggling to mange things went day by day</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">people went worried of what could happen next</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">the time passes and the rain was continuous</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">nothing was in the hand of people but hope of being a things better</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">after a few days rain out to dry&nbsp;</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">people seems to be calm with delightful sight</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #cc0000;\">later the things was back to normal with a view of rain and struggle..&nbsp;</span></i></p>"
                },
