                "title": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "$t": "The journey of Life with endless death"
                },
                "content": {
                    "type": "html",
                    "$t": "<p></p><blockquote><span style=\"background-color: #76a5af;\">The conversation went like this between life and death...</span></blockquote><p></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Life asked the death why people hate you and love me</span></i></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgMs8GNoHfiqAInoWAjzmP0bFtKCf-UQp1ANYT-AxJmAu5Isfln-tubh_xMItUlM0G_nSREprAMRGSRaZoINmqbg3I1KFjDDWnSO-FmIG4zVxg9rV0TU4KbmzNnH-aLXw2XIznhMnz5a3eVPDwljQjvPCSRYq47CdqmGozW_yDVzF_xsEcYnomw_zN7\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"793\" data-original-width=\"1061\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgMs8GNoHfiqAInoWAjzmP0bFtKCf-UQp1ANYT-AxJmAu5Isfln-tubh_xMItUlM0G_nSREprAMRGSRaZoINmqbg3I1KFjDDWnSO-FmIG4zVxg9rV0TU4KbmzNnH-aLXw2XIznhMnz5a3eVPDwljQjvPCSRYq47CdqmGozW_yDVzF_xsEcYnomw_zN7=w565-h239\" width=\"565\" /></a></span></i></div><p></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Death smiled and replied the journey of life is so beautiful</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Life gives endless effort to dream and a option to live</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Life gives a chance to be what you wanted to become</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Life gives a treasury to smile within the several of the corn</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Life uplifts the dream to very height</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Until and unless you get success to survive</span></i></p><p><span style=\"background-color: #e06666;\">Lastly, death said very true meaning of death to a life</span></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Death is a bitter full true for which people are living</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Death gives the sadness which makes people cry</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Death teaches true meaning of living</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Death is death but it don't kills people until and unless they try to survive.&nbsp;</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"background-color: #ffa400; font-size: medium;\">This, way the conversation&nbsp;between life and death got stuck.....</span></i></p>"
                },
