                "title": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "$t": "Destiny the ionic"
                },
                "content": {
                    "type": "html",
                    "$t": "<p><b>Never give up just hold yourself to be one.....</b>&nbsp;</p><p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi3ofakpxHO2fAVwP96Q2YLqp_vYn5-EU4C2G9ZeZljzc-Bogv3LvO8cCeeHqHlHrbQzZj6MnmGOwAc8p5r-WfATf5x6XOQKthp3AtHlcTLddEqJJ7LRs4fMNrDf7ncM3_8NajtoUPZrd02H0J8MugWc_r9JifHr0iwssQY_0oj9mpfujGu-usXz6PP\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"315\" data-original-width=\"474\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi3ofakpxHO2fAVwP96Q2YLqp_vYn5-EU4C2G9ZeZljzc-Bogv3LvO8cCeeHqHlHrbQzZj6MnmGOwAc8p5r-WfATf5x6XOQKthp3AtHlcTLddEqJJ7LRs4fMNrDf7ncM3_8NajtoUPZrd02H0J8MugWc_r9JifHr0iwssQY_0oj9mpfujGu-usXz6PP=w644-h311\" width=\"644\" /></a></div><br /><p></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">I was in the search of destiny&nbsp;</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">So, I decided to find it day and night</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">I cried, I prayed for the destiny to be in my favor alike</span></i></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><i></i></div><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">The day passes and the night, but the time remains aside,</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">In the search of destiny i walked along a mile</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">But nothing i got rather than a shining light</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">I was tired with the time and tides which was for no one with a passing move</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">One day, i looked at the sky and asked why the destiny is not in the favor of mine</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">Than sky looked back with its shining light and said&nbsp;</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">You can get whole world just find the right time and a way to live a life</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">Just work in yourself to find the light that lights inside you not only to get the destiny&nbsp;</span></i></p><p><i><span style=\"color: #674ea7;\">But the whole sky !!!</span></i></p><p><br /></p>"
                },
